`xy` creates a control over a pair of two number values or anything that can be translated to them.

   Builder.xy
       ( { min = 0, max = scene.width, step = 0.1 }
       , { min = 0, max = scene.height, step = 0.1 }
       )
       myModel.lightDirection
       PointLightTo

